        <p>At University Management System, we strive to provide all the information you need to make your academic journey smooth and successful. Here are some of the most common questions we receive, along with our answers:</p>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2>Q: What is the University Management System?</h2>
            <p>A: The University Management System is a comprehensive platform designed to help universities manage academic and administrative tasks efficiently, including course management, student enrollment, grades, and more.</p>
